<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="16" FontFamily="Georgia">
    <Paragraph FontSize="22" FontWeight="Bold">
        Library backup
    </Paragraph>
    
    <Paragraph>
        You can create library backup or restore library from the previous state. 
    </Paragraph>
    
    <Paragraph>
        1. Click "Library backup" context menu item.
    </Paragraph>
    
    <Paragraph>
        2. Choose restore or create mode. 
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        3. Choose folder.
    </Paragraph>
    
    <Paragraph>
        4. Click "Next".
    </Paragraph>   

    <Paragraph>
        If you have some troubles with library backup look at RestoreLibrary.log or CreateBackup.log at Media Glass folder.
    </Paragraph>  
</FlowDocument>
